				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Requirements:
<br />
- Level 65
<br />

<br />
- Required AAs:
<br />
.Minimum:
<br />
Run Speed 3
<br />
Combat Stability 3
<br />
Combat Agility 3
<br />
Natural Durability 3
<br />
Physical Enhancement
<br />

<br />
.Plus 1/3-1/2 of :
<br />
Innate Defense 5
<br />
Lightning Reflexes 5
<br />
Speed of the Knight 3
<br />
Knight's Advantage 3
<br />
Spell Casting Fury 3
<br />
Soul Abrasion 3
<br />
Unholy Touch 3
<br />

<br />
This translate in around 70-100aa as requirement.
<br />

<br />

<br />
- Required Equipment:
<br />
An Instant click buff item (Grim Aura earring, 8th coldain ring, etc)
<br />
Enduring Breath item (Fishbone earring, Shissar eye earring, Lodizal shield, Amulet of Grey Waste, etc)
<br />
Circlet of Shadow (the insta cast one)
<br />

<br />
Resist Gear: 100ish to all resists unbuffed would be ok. If you can manage to get any given single resist to 400-450 with full buffs+bard song, then you may survive some fights.
<br />

<br />
1200ac/5000hp would be around the minimum for gears requirement. If you cant survive the attack of a mob doubling for 600ish, you cant off tank much for us.
<br />

<br />

<br />
- Required Flags:
<br />
.Very Basic Minimum :
<br />
Plane of Valor/Storms (must have completed a PoJ trial)
<br />
Bastion of Thunder (must have the Talisman of Thunderous Foyer on your keyring)
<br />
Crypt of Decay (must have killed Grummus)
<br />
Plane of Tactics (must have killed Manaetic Behemoth)
<br />
Plane of Nightmare Hedge quest (the 3 groups thing)
<br />
Terris Thule
<br />

<br />

<br />
.I will h8 you if you dont have those, but still may be willing to talk going with my mood :
<br />
Agnarr
<br />
Halls of Honor Trials (all 3 plz)
<br />
Mithaniel Marr
<br />
Lower Crypt of Decay
<br />
Bertoxxulous
<br />
Tallon Zek
<br />
Vallon Zek
<br />
Tylis Newleaf
<br />
Saryn
<br />

<br />

<br />
- Must not be stupid :
<br />
Stupid newbs make me cry  
<br />

<br />

<br />
We raid most days of the week (5-6/7).
<br />
From 6PM CST to Midnightish on weekdays and 1PM CST to who-the-hell-knows on weekends.
<br />
You must attend 75% of our raids.
<br />
Our raids are mandatory : if you are online and can join the raid, you must join it.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Send me a tell in game, or to Brdayar, or post here, whatever. 
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
magelo E/V
<br />

